{"about_the_game":"In the bleak 1920s, luck abandons you, gripped by debt and entangled by the local gangster, Mr. Blackwood. Your path veers to the accursed seaside town of Innsmouth, where a hidden treasure is rumored to lie within Devil Reef.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/left_header.png?t=1734969465\" /> <strong>Embark solo or with companions</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/right_header.png?t=1734969465\" /> <br>Ferry to Devil Reef alone or with friends \u2014 let the journey begin.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/BeachGIF.gif?t=1734969465\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/left_header.png?t=1734969465\" /> <strong>Explore Devil Reef and its horrors</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/right_header.png?t=1734969465\" /><br>What is thought to be an effortless treasure hunt changes fast as you venture deeper, amassing gold. The once-promising labyrinth reveals its sinister nature. Corridors contort, and eldritch horrors multiply, presenting a daunting challenge. Are you strong enough to reach the mythic treasure at the bottom of Devil Reef?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/ActionGIF.gif?t=1734969465\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/left_header.png?t=1734969465\" /> <strong>Unlock powerful weapons and upgrades</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/right_header.png?t=1734969465\" /> <br>Bolster your chances for survival with arcane scrolls and incantations. Unlock and enhance weapons to confront the impending otherworldly battle ahead. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/Upgrades_InncantationsGIF.gif?t=1734969465\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/left_header.png?t=1734969465\" /> <strong>Key features</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/right_header.png?t=1734969465\" /> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Isometric action roguelike gameplay <br></li><li>Up to 4 player online co-op multiplayer<br></li><li>Unlock weapons and upgrades to progress further<br></li><li>Atmospheric soundtrack and effects<br></li><li>Wide range of Incantations boosts and give you new abilities<br></li><li>Generative dungeons - Three Acts with unique bosses will be added during early access<br></li><li>Map Editor for custom player created maps - Will be added during early access</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/left_header.png?t=1734969465\" /> <strong>Plunge Into the Abyss!</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/right_header.png?t=1734969465\" /> <br>Prepare for a chilling journey into the heart of darkness with Devil Reef, an action-packed roguelike co-op dungeon crawler developed by The Fine Arc Nordic AB. Immerse yourself in a haunting universe inspired by H.P. Lovecraft's twisted tales, where pixel-art graphics and atmospheric soundscapes pay homage to the golden era of 90s gaming - <strong><i>Wishlist now!</i></strong><br><br>Join the discussion on the Steam Forums or dive into the abyss on our Discord Server (link available in the side panel).<br><br><img cl